description: This file is a header file defining internal API functions for the Http Ato FxCat1 object, including function prototypes for creating code and name tables, and retrieving atom codes and names.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat1CreateCodeTable
methods.description: Creates a code table for the Http Ato FxCat1 object.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat1CreateNameTable
methods.description: Creates a name table for the Http Ato FxCat1 object.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat1GetAtomCode
methods.description: Retrieves the atom code corresponding to a given name.

methods.name: HttpAtoFxCat1GetAtomName
methods.description: Retrieves the atom name corresponding to a given code.
